| NR-03 | Employee Grade/Level determines Accommodation rate (Level 2 to 3H have different amounts) | Transcript §48:55–§50:36 | Per Diem/Accommodation must be grade-linked. New data entity: Employee Grade. Impacts EP-03, EP-05, EP-06. | ADD to EP-NEW-02 + EP-03 |
| NR-04 | Destination-based pricing matrix — rates differ by destination (e.g., Darfur higher rate) | Transcript §53:04–§53:49 + MoM Open Item 1 | Configurable destination pricing. Impacts Travel Cost Review. | CONFIRM with MTN Sudan — OPEN ITEM |
