# SECTION 4 — UPDATED WORKFLOW (Post-Backlog Analysis)

The following workflow replaces all prior workflow diagrams. It incorporates the HR step confirmed in the second meeting transcript.

## 4.1 Updated Confirmed Workflow

| **Step** | **Stage** | **Actor** | **Applies To** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Mission Request | Assigned Person | All |
| 2 | Line Manager Approval | Line Manager | All |
| 3 | Division Manager / GM Approval | Division Manager | All |
| 3A | HR Approval [NEW — International Only] | HR Team | International Only |
| 3B | HR Notification [NEW — National Only] | System → HR Email | National Only |
| 4 | Travel Team Review | Travel Team | All |
| 5 | GL Review [CORRECTED — precedes Treasury] | GL Team | All |
| 6 | Treasury Payment | Treasury Team | All |
| 7 | Mission Active | System (Auto) | All |
| 8* | Mission Extension (Optional — repeats steps 2–7) | Assigned Person initiates | Optional |
| 9 | Mission Closure | Assigned Person | All |
| 10 | Finance Settlement | Finance Team | All |
| 11 | Mission Completed | System (Auto) | All |

* Step 8 (Extension) follows the same full approval cycle as the original mission (Steps 2–7) per MoM §10.

## 4.2 Mission Statuses (Complete List)

| **Status** | **Description** | **Source** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Draft | Saved but not submitted | Travel_System_Req |
| Pending Line Manager Approval | Submitted; awaiting LM | Travel_System_Req |
| Pending Division Manager Approval | LM approved; awaiting DM | Travel_System_Req |
| Pending HR Approval [NEW] | DM approved; awaiting HR (International only) | Transcript 11/06/2026 |
| Pending Travel Review | All approvals done; awaiting Travel Team | Travel_System_Req |
| Pending GL Review [NEW Status Label] | Travel review done; awaiting GL Team | MoM Confirmed Workflow |
| Pending Payment | GL approved; awaiting Treasury | Travel_System_Req |
| Mission Active | Payment confirmed; mission underway | Travel_System_Req |
| Mission Extended | Extension approved and paid | Travel_System_Req |
| Mission Closed | Closure submitted; pending settlement | Travel_System_Req |
| Pending Settlement | Awaiting Finance settlement | Travel_System_Req |
| Completed | Settlement done; mission fully closed | Travel_System_Req |
| Rejected | Rejected at any approval stage | MoM Notes |
| Cancelled [NEW — MISSING INFO] | MISSING INFORMATION — Cancellation rules not defined | Transcript §52:24 |

# SECTION 5 — TFS-READY USER STORIES (Key New & Updated Stories)

Full user stories below follow the standard format. Only new and updated stories are shown; existing stories in the original backlog retain their structure.

## US-EP04-LM-001 — Approve Mission Request (Line Manager)

| **Title** | Approve Mission Request — Line Manager |
| --- | --- |
| As a | Line Manager |
| I want to | review and approve or reject a mission request submitted by an Assigned Person |
| So that | the mission can proceed to Division Manager approval |
| **Acceptance Criteria** | Given I am logged in as Line Manager; When I open Pending Approvals; Then I see all missions pending my approval with Mission ID, Employee Name, Destination, Dates, Type; When I click Approve with optional note; Then status changes to Pending Division Manager Approval and DM is notified by email; When I click Reject with mandatory note; Then status changes to Rejected and Assigned Person is notified. |
| Priority | HIGH |
| Source | MoM Confirmed Workflow + MoM §5 |
| Dev Status | READY FOR DEVELOPMENT |

## [NEW] US-EP-NEW01-HR-001 — HR Approval of International Mission

| **Title** | [NEW] HR Approve International Mission |
| --- | --- |
| As a | HR Team Member |
| I want to | review and approve or reject an International mission after Division Manager approval |
| So that | International missions have HR sign-off before Travel Review proceeds |
| **Acceptance Criteria** | Given I am logged in as HR; When an International mission is approved by DM; Then I see it in my Pending Approvals; When I Approve; Then status = Pending Travel Review and Travel Team is notified; When I Reject; Then status = Rejected and Assigned Person is notified. |
| Priority | HIGH |
| Source | Transcript 11/06/2026 §4:06–§11:21 |
| **Dev Status** | NEEDS CLARIFICATION — Workflow position of HR approval step must be formally confirmed by MTN Sudan. Is HR before or after DM? Is HR involved in National missions at all? |

## [NEW] US-EP-NEW02-GRD-001 — Grade-Based Accommodation Rate

| **Title** | [NEW] Apply Grade-Based Accommodation Rate at Mission Creation |
| --- | --- |
| As a | Travel Team Member |
| I want to | see the accommodation cost automatically calculated based on the employee's grade level |
| So that | Travel Review accurately reflects the correct allowance for each employee's grade |
| **Business Rule** | Accommodation rate varies by employee grade (Level 2 to Level 3H). Exact rates to be provided by MTN Sudan. |
| Source | Transcript 11/06/2026 §48:55–§50:36 |
| **Dev Status** | BLOCKED — Grade levels and rate matrix not yet provided by MTN Sudan (MoM Open Item 1 related). |

## [UPDATED] US-EP08-EXT-001 — Mission Extension Recalculation

| **Title** | [UPDATED] Recalculate Costs on Mission Extension |
| --- | --- |
| As a | Assigned Person |
| I want to | submit a mission extension with a new end date and have Per Diem and Accommodation recalculated |
| So that | the extension accurately reflects the additional cost for the extended period |
| **Acceptance Criteria** | Given mission status = Mission Active; When I submit an extension with New End Date; Then system calculates extension days = New End Date - Current End Date; Then Per Diem recalculates for extension days; Then Accommodation recalculates for extension nights; Then new total is displayed for Travel Review; Then Extended By field records my user ID and timestamp. |
| Source | MoM §10 |
| Dev Status | NEEDS CLARIFICATION — Per Diem and Accommodation formulas not yet provided (MoM Open Items 2 & 3). |

