# SECTION 8 — UAT SCENARIOS (New & Updated)

## UAT-EP04-LM-001 — Line Manager Approves Mission

| **Preconditions** | Mission exists in status 'Pending Line Manager Approval'. User logged in as Line Manager. |
| --- | --- |
| Step 1 | Navigate to Pending Approvals. |
| Step 2 | Select the mission. View details. |
| Step 3 | Click Approve. Add optional note. Confirm. |
| **Expected Result** | Mission status = Pending Division Manager Approval. DM receives email notification. Mission no longer appears in LM pending list. |
| **Negative Test** | Reject without entering a reason → system should prevent rejection and show validation error. |

## [NEW] UAT-EP-NEW01-HR-001 — HR Approves International Mission

| **Preconditions** | International Mission in status 'Pending HR Approval'. User logged in as HR Team Member. |
| --- | --- |
| Step 1 | Navigate to Pending Approvals (HR view). |
| Step 2 | Review mission details including destination, employee, dates, type. |
| Step 3 | Click Approve. Mission progresses. |
| **Expected Result** | Mission status = Pending Travel Review. Travel Team receives email notification. |
| **Edge Case** | National Mission should NOT appear in HR Pending Approvals — only notification sent. Verify HR cannot take action on National missions. |

## [UPDATED] UAT-EP08-EXT-001 — Mission Extension Recalculates Costs

| **Preconditions** | Mission in status 'Mission Active'. Pricing matrix configured. User = Assigned Person. |
| --- | --- |
| Step 1 | Navigate to Mission Extensions. Click Request Extension. |
| Step 2 | Enter New End Date (later than current end). Enter Extension Reason. |
| Step 3 | System calculates extension days and shows new Per Diem + Accommodation totals. Submit. |
| **Expected Result** | Extension request enters approval chain (LM → DM → HR if International → Travel → GL → Treasury). 'Extended By' field records submitting user and timestamp. |
| **Negative Test** | Enter New End Date earlier than current end date → validation error. System must reject. |

